movie_name: Truth and Lies: The Last Gangster
short_description: The two-hour event special on the infamous Gambino mob family, featuring a new interview with one of the most notorious hitmen in mafia history, "Sammy "The Bull" Gravano.

short_description: On 11 March 2004, 3 days before Spain's general elections, a series of bombings against 4 trains in Madrid killed 193 people and injured around 2,000. This documentary explains the reactions and investigations that took place after.
